/a><br />\n推呀！<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/Stand_with_HK/status/1196133437251506178?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FStand_with_HK%2Fstatus%2F1196133437251506178%3Fs%3D20&d=iNjGaRjC%2BmHxaGo4xJJZV4eonPPUtn1HApnj2AcFxYA%3D&h=57c23e20\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FStand_with_HK%2Fstatus%2F1196133437251506178%3Fs%3D20&h=c994d01d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/Stand_with_HK/status/1196133437251506178?s=20</a><br />\n眾志<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/demosisto/status/1196112617892220928?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fdemosisto%2Fstatus%2F1196112617892220928%3Fs%3D21&d=iNjGaRjC%2BmHxaGo4xJJZV4eonPPUtn1HApnj2AcFxYA%3D&h=23c9fdfb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fdemosisto%2Fstatus%2F1196112617892220928%3Fs%3D21&h=bd4340c9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/demosisto/status/1196112617892220928?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n警察暴行<br />\n克警用示威者頭部撞擊石屎地<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hkdnow1/status/1196316374781419520?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhkdnow1%2Fstatus%2F1196316374781419520%3Fs%3D21&d=iNjGaRjC%2BmHxaGo4xJJZV4eonPPUtn1HApnj2AcFxYA%3D&h=dabc1ef6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhkdnow1%2Fstatus%2F1196316374781419520%3Fs%3D21&h=e2b5b9c6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/hkdnow1/status/1196316374781419520?s=21</a><br />\n眾志講警察拖示威者之後再兜頭踩<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/demosisto/status/1196392281432977408?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fdemosisto%2Fstatus%2F1196392281432977408%3Fs%3D21&d=iNjGaRjC%2BmHxaGo4xJJZV4eonPPUtn1HApnj2AcFxYA%3D&h=f0617278\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fdemosisto%2Fstatus%2F1196392281432977408%3Fs%3D21&h=ff015117\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/demosisto/status/1196392281432977408?s=21</a><br />\n克警踢頭<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/nathanlawkc/status/1196193334194319367?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fnathanlawkc%2Fstatus%2F1196193334194319367%3Fs%3D21&d=iNjGaRjC%2BmHxaGo4xJJZV4eonPPUtn1HApnj2AcFxYA%3D&h=a729dc0f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fnathanlawkc%2Fstatus%2F1196193334194319367%3Fs%3D21&h=79bf8464\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/nathanlawkc/status/1196193334194319367?s=21</a><br />\n講警察當醫生護士fa係犯人,全部反鎖雙手<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/joshuawongcf/status/1196107736779354114?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fjoshuawongcf%2Fstatus%2F1196107736779354114%3Fs%3D20&d=iNjGaRjC%2BmHxaGo4xJJZV4eonPPUtn1HApnj2AcFxYA%3D&h=a8dcc235\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fjoshuawongcf%2Fstatus%2F1196107736779354114%3Fs%3D20&h=723549c6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/joshuawongcf/status/1196107736779354114?s=20</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/nathanlawkc/status/1196107058136961025?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fnathanlawkc%2Fstatus%2F1196107058136961025%3Fs%3D21&d=iNjGaRjC%2BmHxaGo4xJJZV4eonPPUtn1HApnj2AcFxYA%3D&h=5c6780d7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fnathanlawkc%2Fstatus%2F1196107058136961025%3Fs%3D21&h=a023b2b1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/nathanlawkc/status/1196107058136961025?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\n人權法案情況<br />\n美國參議院啟動「熱線」機制推進參議院版本的《香港人權與民主法案》（下稱香港人權法）。倘獲參議院通過，參眾兩院其後需要啟動「和解程序」，將兩個版本香港人權法合二為一，交由總統特朗普（Donald Trump）簽署生效。不過，特朗普其實可以動用「總統否決權」（Presidential Vetoes），令香港人權法不會生效。而在此情況下，國會亦有權推翻特朗普的對香港人權法的否決。<br />\n倘香港人權法獲通過，特朗普有甚麼選項？<br />\n（1）特朗普可在10日內（除周日以外）簽署協議，令香港人權法生效；<br />\n<br />\n（2）特朗普可不簽署法案，並在10日內（除周日以外）撰寫異議書（a statement of objections），再交回國會重審；<br />\n<br />\n（3）特朗普可選擇甚麼都不做，若該時並非國會的休會期，法案會在10日後就自動生效；<br />\n<br />\n（4）若香港人權法送達特朗普後，國會在10日內（除周日以外）休會，而特朗普選擇甚麼都不做，此法案會自動失效，這被稱為「口袋否決」（pocket veto）。<br />\n<br />\n若特朗普拒絕簽署，國會可怎樣？<br />\n國會可動議推翻特朗普的否決，倘在參眾兩院都獲得3分2的票數支持，就能推翻特朗普的否決權。特朗普必須接受國會的決定。"},{"pid":"2ba36326e98e30cc0cb4a93c360fe199f62dc2e3","tid":1736403,"uid":208765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T17:50:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6d063b20dc135c6ce1b2b58e27f87276cfbefc4","tid":1736403,"uid":208765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T17:51:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aac274b727912a0362929c1b6b8bc277ef2d5d03","tid":1736403,"uid":118715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T18:01:32.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"5b2247b8bdf1a151d77561b9b277fa60da84327e","tid":1736403,"uid":57221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T18:07:47.000Z","msg":"p"},{"pid":"0eaeae43acbd26b8afa79b6f9181a4ce9756f0a8","tid":1736403,"uid":304193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T18:08:45.000Z","msg":"我p牌好似唔會推得起。。。<br />\n如果你覺得有用，我唔介意你地copy內容開新page<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"752bd7cd08513ac5ca555f944a9fa5f811c5a53a","tid":1736403,"uid":304193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T18:13:19.000Z","msg":"係就快啦，其他手足準備訓教。。。🙈"},{"pid":"7072c4f44fb0ba6ed75efb7f57a4fdccccdb4830","tid":1736403,"uid":247798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-